latestIgtvVideos.title: A DAY IN KERALA 🌴🌊🥥
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Here's a glimpse of my vacay in Kerala! It was a short break that I desperately needed to refresh and get some clarity in my life. 🌴
Just in case you're wondering, these are the places I visited on that day: • St. George's Forane Church (Sooo beautiful)
• Lulu Mall (Sparky's Amusement center caught my attention) 🙈
And the Metro Station. 🙆🏻‍♀️
Also, this is my first proper IGTV video. 
So yayyyyy!!!! ⭐

This beloved 90-year-old bakery from Mumbai has now opened its doors in Bangalore 🥨🍰🥯

Known for its irresistible puffs and freshly baked pizzas, this charming spot has so much more to offer. What truly caught my eye was their impressive variety of desserts. It’s incredible how this bakery manages to keep everything not only affordable but also bursting with authentic, mouthwatering flavors. 🫶🏻

If you’re in the mood for something sweet or savory, this place has it all, and it’s sure to satisfy every craving.
